parameters:
\nc<Anchor>The turmoil that struck at the end of last year has finally
begun to settle down.

\nc<Anchor>While the Hero Association is apprehending and punishing
those involved, they are also advancing the treatment of
women who have been turned into succubi...

\nc<Saki>That former hero customer... I can't believe he really
helped us. I'm glad I decided to contact him, even though it
was a long shot.
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>My hips were a little sore after going at it again, though.

\nc<Senpai>President, the first patient targeted for treatment has been
successfully discharged.

\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>Ahh, please feel free to call me casually when it's just the
two of us. I'm not used to being called 'President'.
\nc<Saki>Especially when it's Meary-senpai calling me that...
\nc<Senpai>Understood. To be honest, it was awkward for me too.
\nc<>The news flows like background music through the screen...

\nc<Anchor>On the other hand, since the discovery of a customer's death
accident, the First Succubus Industry has made clear its
stance on extracting essence using safer methods...
\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>You really convinced them well. Good job, senpai.

\nc<Senpai>Well, when you've been in this job for a long time, you
learn how rough other contractors can be, whether you like
it or not...

\nc<Senpai>There are many things that would cause quite a stir if they
became known to the public.

\nc<Saki>Everyone is desperate to meet their quotas... All the forced
dispatch locations have been closed down, right?

\nc<Senpai>That was the first thing we did. All the dispatched workers
are undergoing treatment now.

\bustMsgExp[1, 3]\nc<Saki>That's good to hear. Though not everyone will be able to
return to their previous lives.

\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>...By the way, is that okay? The crucial Saki can't receive
treatment.

\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>Yes, I've already been promoted to Succubus Queen, so it's
impossible for me to go back to being human now.
\bustMsgExp[1, 3]\nc<Saki>But that's alright. I've actually come to enjoy this job.

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>Still, I'd like you to refrain from frequently disguising
yourself as an ordinary employee and going out.

\nc<Saki>Can't I do it just occasionally? It's like an exclusive
lucky service from First Succubus Industry...

\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>...It's been a while since we've had this kind of
overtime.\bustMsgExp[2, 0]Well, alright.
